      <title>价格飙升，澳大利亚黄金投资者期待并购浪潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/soaring-prices-have-australian-gold-bugs-expecting-m-a-splurge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受今年贵金属创纪录涨幅的提振，澳大利亚黄金行业正期待着一波交易浪潮，由于勘探工作滞后，小型矿商将成为目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/soaring-prices-have-australian-gold-bugs-expecting-m-a-splurge</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 02:37:34 GMT</pubDate>
