    <item>
      <title>恒大清盘人对普华永道提起法律诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/evergrande-liquidators-start-legal-action-against-pwc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国恒大集团清算人已对普华永道会计师事务所提起诉讼，这是其采取的又一法律措施，旨在从该房地产巨头手中收回至少部分债权人的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/evergrande-liquidators-start-legal-action-against-pwc</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 02:03:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日央行行长内田缓解利率担忧，日元兑美元下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/yen-extends-losses-against-dollar-as-market-volatility-continues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本央行副行长内田新一表示如果金融市场不稳定，政策制定者将不会提高基准利率之后，日元兑美元周三延续跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/yen-extends-losses-against-dollar-as-market-volatility-continues</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 01:49:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
