    <item>
      <title>野村证券的威尔科克斯谈全球市场、日本央行和公司战略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-07/nomura-s-willcox-on-global-markets-boj-firm-s-strategy-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[野村控股公司执行官兼批发业务主管 Christopher Willcox 分享了他对全球金融市场持续动荡、日本和美国经济状况以及央行政策的看法。他还讨论了野村的战略及其前景。他在“彭博：亚洲贸易”上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-07/nomura-s-willcox-on-global-markets-boj-firm-s-strategy-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 00:01:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行行长内田缓解利率担忧后，日本股市飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/japan-s-stock-futures-signal-lower-open-as-market-stays-on-edge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行副行长内田新一表示，在市场不稳定时央行不会加息，导致日元走弱，日本股市飙升，扭转了早前的跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/japan-s-stock-futures-signal-lower-open-as-market-stays-on-edge</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 23:35:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>野村证券的威尔科克斯表示，套利交易有更多放松空间，证明日本央行的做法是正确的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/nomura-s-willcox-says-boj-s-rate-hike-has-been-vindicated</link>
      <description><![CDATA[野村控股公司一位高管表示，日本央行上周加息的决定是恰当的，如果等待更长时间，套利交易的平仓对金融市场的冲击将会更大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/nomura-s-willcox-says-boj-s-rate-hike-has-been-vindicated</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 23:34:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场关注伊朗袭击事件，风险偏好上升，油价持稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者关注伊朗对以色列的报复性打击，油价从全球市场暴跌中恢复后保持稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 23:29:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行缓解利率担忧后亚洲股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行副行长表示，如果市场不稳定，日本央行将不会加息，此言一出，亚洲股市出现上涨，安抚了因近期日元飙升而感到不安的投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 22:38:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
